io.outofprintmagazine.nlp

Class Analyzer

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.outofprintmagazine.nlp.Analyzer

  • public class Analyzer
extends Object

    The main library execution entry point for oopcorenlp.

    analyze runs the coreNLP annotators, runs the custom annotators, serializes the annotation tree, and returns four JsonDocuments: STANFORD, OOP, AGGREGATES, PIPELINE

    Author:
    Ram Sadasiv
    See Also:
    CoreNlpUtils, OOPAnnotator, CoreNlpSerializer, Serializer
